WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.216 --> 00:00:10.100
 James Cameron's view of the ROLEX DEEPSEA CHALLENGE watch 

00:00:23.687 --> 00:00:26.185
 As we are preparing to set sail for this feat 

00:00:26.305 --> 00:00:28.955
 This Deepsea Challenge watch is just in our hands. 

00:00:29.075 --> 00:00:32.750
 I took it and couldn’t help but show appreciation. 

00:00:32.870 --> 00:00:37.278
 It’s very difficult to create a new watch in five weeks. 

00:00:37.313 --> 00:00:40.111
 Especially this is used for deep sea exploration 

00:00:40.149 --> 00:00:45.383
 I watched the watch structure carefully. 

00:00:45.393 --> 00:00:48.631
 I really admire the watchmaking team to complete the task so quickly. 

00:00:48.751 --> 00:00:53.935
 I have always respected the exquisite craftsmanship and ingenious design. 

00:00:53.963 --> 00:00:58.915
 From conceiving new ideas to completing computer-aided design (CAD) 

00:00:58.952 --> 00:01:02.124
 Then through the processable process 

00:01:02.152 --> 00:01:04.069
 Direct use of digital command (NC) machines 

00:01:04.109 --> 00:01:07.377
 Then the whole process of making prototypes is really amazing. 

00:01:19.739 --> 00:01:22.716
 It seems that the number is small 

00:01:22.836 --> 00:01:25.787
 Very active and experienced team 

00:01:25.907 --> 00:01:30.523
 Do things that others think are impossible in a very short time 

00:01:30.786 --> 00:01:34.008
 Whether I saw it in the submarine and this watch, I realized this. 

00:01:51.061 --> 00:01:53.028
 This is an extraordinary experience 

00:01:53.064 --> 00:01:57.207
 Because we uphold the same values 

00:01:57.528 --> 00:02:02.664
 Strive for perfection, precision and quality 

00:02:02.784 --> 00:02:06.594
 And at the same time have a spirit of adventure 

00:02:06.631 --> 00:02:08.716
 Be brave in pioneering and innovating 

00:02:16.137 --> 00:02:19.977
 I have worn Rolex watches for more than a quarter of a century. 

00:02:20.097 --> 00:02:23.503
 Look at it less than 10,000 times 

00:02:23.521 --> 00:02:26.217
 However, it now makes me look good 

